19. saying. that Churches are dedicated with the signe
of the crosse, where he not onely chaunged the worde

                  charactere into mysterio, but also translated the worde
mysterio, by the signe: where he confesseth his fault, he
may be pardoned, but where he iustifieth mysterio and
sign
