dalie vpō ye word expresse scripture, either he answereth
not to ye same thing wherof he is demanded, or else he
knoweth not yt an argument rightly concluded out of
holy scripture, is as good as ye very words of ye scripture,
as when I say, if Peter beleued &amp; was baptized ergo, he
was saued, is as true, as these words, whosoeuer beleueth
